conformance.naming

Class DeletionTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • test.Test
      • conformance.naming.NamingTest
        • conformance.naming.DeletionTest

  • public class DeletionTest
extends NamingTest
    Tests naming server delete method.

    This test starts two storage servers, and registers them with the naming server. It then checks that the naming server correctly commands the storage servers to delete both files and directories, when the naming server is asked to do so. In order to ensure that the file is present on both storage servers, the naming server accesses it enough times to cause the file to be replicated.
